0.08    16 Dec 2008
        * fix bug in Store->expire_ticket() where cookie not found

0.09    xxx
        * set REMOTE_ADDR to $c->req->address if $c->req->address != REMOTE_ADDR.
          This fixes bug when running dev server behind proxy (similar to fcgi).

